// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3090 — Mass File Rename (clop)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 44bd711b-57bb-5d82-aba0-67fd2d1852bd

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
